{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't go into it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The fact is that it's now going to be published by the Mandelbaum House, attached to the University of Sydney.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was probably going, possibly, by the end of this month to Sydney, to finalize the conditions of the publication.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it will, in all probability, be published by the middle of this year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it has been judged by the authorities in this field at Hebrew University, and at Oxford, and so on, as a suitable textbook for undergraduate and postgraduates in the English-speaking world.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's going to be published.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but-- but maybe not to the same extent as people who've-- who lived through it in camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For-- I-- I made sure that, on top of what they learned at school-- they went, both, to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, at [NON-ENGLISH] and at the time, when they had came there, when they arrived there, [NON-ENGLISH] already had a course in Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Shoah was-- the Holocaust was part of that course, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, I've discussed with them and I've elaborated it, but not with-- from the perspective, the angle of depressing them, of-- of making them feel that-- that the vibrations of this tragedy are still touching them in a personal way.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted them to understand it in the context of the totality of Jewish history, and understand it as a part of the imponderables of history generally, and the imponderables of the Jewish history, which had so many crises in its 5,000 years.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You may be surprised by my answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, all my life, never looking backwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
